---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro'
import Button from '@/components/Button.astro'
import JSIcon from '@/icons/JavaScript.svg'
---

<Layout title="404 - Página no encontrada" noindex>
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[70vh] text-center pt-24 pb-12">
    <Container class="items-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <h1
          class="text-8xl md:text-[12rem] font-clash font-bold text-white leading-none tracking-tighter flex items-center"
        >
          4
          <div class="relative size-16 md:size-24 ml-2 pl-2">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 blur-2xl opacity-40 bg-javascript rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="relative animate-bounce [&>svg]:w-full [&>svg]:h-full">
              <JSIcon class="rounded-full" />
            </div>
          </div>
          4
        </h1>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-clash text-javascript mb-8">
        ReferenceError: Page is not defined
      </h2>

      <p class="text-light-gray text-lg md:text-xl max-w-lg mb-12">
        Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe. Parece que se ha quedado perdida en el <span
          class="text-white font-mono">event loop</span
        > o ha sido recolectada por el <span class="text-white font-mono">garbage collector</span>.
      </p>

      <Button href="/" style="yellow"> Volver al inicio </Button>
    </Container>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(247, 223, 30, 0.2);
  }
</style>
